text: Md. Kamruzzaman is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Jhenaidah-1. ==Career== Kamruzzaman was elected to parliament from Jhenaidah-1 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1986. ==References== Category:Awami League politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Jhenaidah District
